    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014honestly, it feels just like it's fresh off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service milestone. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that 'new car' magic. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for a great new home for it. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come by and take a look\u2014I'd love to show it to you!",
