    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered legend, maintained to a standard that satisfies the most discerning collector. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and has undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing service to ensure mechanical longevity. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with a reinforced rear subframe and a suspension geometry that retains its factory-spec rigidity and damping. Finished in original paint with documented depth readings, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience with no mechanical compromises.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Clean title. Low mileage. Full service history included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
