    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in flawless condition that must be seen to be appreciated. The original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirls, chips, or imperfections, having been protected by a professional ceramic coating and kept in a climate-controlled garage since new. Inside, the cabin remains in a pristine state; the premium leather seats are supple with no signs of wear, and the dashboard and trim are completely free of sun damage or rattles. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively by master technicians using only OEM parts, with a comprehensive binder of records documenting its pampered life. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning enthusiast to own a benchmark-quality example that drives as smoothly as it looks. No accidents, no modifications, and a strictly smoke-free, pet-free history.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
