      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You seriously won't believe how gorgeous this car is. I've babied it from day one, and it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single scratch or dent to be found\u2014it's truly in pristine condition. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage its whole life. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is the one! Come take it for a spin, I promise you're going to fall in love! \u2728",
